  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "It gets hard, yeah it gets hard, you know When it's on you and under your control And time just runs on it's own, yeah it gets hard, you get up, you get hard For a part of the show, yeah, it is a part of the show Oh, I know that you wanted this to last I know that you wanted it to be special But it's not, oh fuck no it's not Oh, you trip around me and all you wanna be I don't want you around, can't you see when I tell you to leave Just leave, leave me alone, when the nights are on Don't think about me when you're all alone Don't, don't, just don't Cause we all know where it goes when you do, when you do I don't want that, I don't want trips I don't want some rages and sacrifices, I just want I just want Nothing to do with it, no love, no grudges I just want a place of real unity Just take that right back away And take the violence away from me Oh, you are just not it You want to be here and I'm sorry I gave you any idea But I don't need it, you don't know me But you probably need me, I'm sorry Spirit, I can't take no more The kid is gone, he's gone Oh, it's a beast, go sing Get over it, go back That's what you're owed And I make it what I know But it's so hard to deny Genius inside, genius around But you just gotta understand Don't want you around Don't want you around",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 17.239999771118164,
      "text": "It gets hard, yeah it gets hard, you know When it's on you and under your control",
      "start": 7.159999847412109
    },
    {
      "end": 26.84000015258789,
      "text": "And time just runs on it's own, yeah it gets hard, you get up, you get hard",
      "start": 18.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 32.220001220703125,
      "text": "For a part of the show, yeah, it is a part of the show",
      "start": 26.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 39.540000915527344,
      "text": "Oh, I know that you wanted this to last I know that you wanted it to be special",
      "start": 32.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 43.540000915527344,
      "text": "But it's not, oh fuck no it's not",
      "start": 39.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 49.619998931884766,
      "text": "Oh, you trip around me and all you wanna be",
      "start": 46.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 53.81999969482422,
      "text": "I don't want you around, can't you see when I tell you to leave",
      "start": 49.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 59.15999984741211,
      "text": "Just leave, leave me alone, when the nights are on",
      "start": 54.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 62.7599983215332,
      "text": "Don't think about me when you're all alone",
      "start": 59.15999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 65.77999877929688,
      "text": "Don't, don't, just don't",
      "start": 62.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 72.12000274658203,
      "text": "Cause we all know where it goes when you do, when you do",
      "start": 65.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 76.12000274658203,
      "text": "I don't want that, I don't want trips",
      "start": 72.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 79.94000244140625,
      "text": "I don't want some rages and sacrifices, I just want",
      "start": 76.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 83.83999633789062,
      "text": "I just want",
      "start": 81.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 89.0999984741211,
      "text": "Nothing to do with it, no love, no grudges",
      "start": 85.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 92.81999969482422,
      "text": "I just want a place of real unity",
      "start": 89.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 95.18000030517578,
      "text": "Just take that right back away",
      "start": 92.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 99.13999938964844,
      "text": "And take the violence away from me",
      "start": 96.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 102.4000015258789,
      "text": "Oh, you are just not it",
      "start": 99.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 107.58000183105469,
      "text": "You want to be here and I'm sorry",
      "start": 102.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 111.69999694824219,
      "text": "I gave you any idea",
      "start": 108.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 115.4800033569336,
      "text": "But I don't need it, you don't know me",
      "start": 112
    },
    {
      "end": 118.4000015258789,
      "text": "But you probably need me, I'm sorry",
      "start": 115.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 121.27999877929688,
      "text": "Spirit, I can't take no more",
      "start": 118.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 125.66000366210938,
      "text": "The kid is gone, he's gone",
      "start": 121.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 127.69999694824219,
      "text": "Oh, it's a beast, go sing",
      "start": 125.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 129.5,
      "text": "Get over it, go back",
      "start": 127.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 131.0800018310547,
      "text": "That's what you're owed",
      "start": 129.5
    },
    {
      "end": 133,
      "text": "And I make it what I know",
      "start": 131.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 135.77999877929688,
      "text": "But it's so hard to deny",
      "start": 133
    },
    {
      "end": 138.77999877929688,
      "text": "Genius inside, genius around",
      "start": 135.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 141.10000610351562,
      "text": "But you just gotta understand",
      "start": 138.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 143.25999450683594,
      "text": "Don't want you around",
      "start": 141.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 152.3800048828125,
      "text": "Don't want you around",
      "start": 151.0399932861328
    }
